Package gov.nasa.gsfc.spdf.ssc

Provides a Web Service interface to NASA's Satellite Situation Center (http://sscweb.gsfc.nasa.gov/).

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
SatelliteSituationCenterInterface This interface represents the XML Web Service interface to NASA's Satellite Situation Center.
 

Class Summary
BFieldModelOptions This class represents B field model options.
BFieldModelParameters This class represents B field model parameters.
BFieldTraceOptions This class represents "B field trace" listing options.
BTraceData This class represents B-field trace data.
CoordinateData This class represents satellite coordinate data.
CoordinateOptions This class represents coordinate system component options.
DataFileRequest This class represents a listing request for the SatelliteSituationCenterInterface.getDataFiles(DataFileRequest) method.
DataRequest This class represents a request for information from the Satellite Situation Center.
DataResult This class represents the result of a DataRequest to the Satellite Situation Center.
DistanceFromOptions This class represents "distance from" listing options.
FileResult This class represents the result of a Request to the Satellite Situation Center.
FilteredCoordinateOptions This class represents coordinate system component options that include location filters.
FormatOptions This class represents output format and units options.
GraphFormatOptions This class represents formating options for an SSC graph request.
GraphLabelOptions This class represents custom label options for an SSC graph request.
GraphOptions This class represents options for an SSC graphing request.
GraphRequest This class represents a request for a graph from the Satellite Situation Center.
GraphScale This class represents manual scale values for an SSC graphing request.
GroundStationDescription This class represents a description of a ground station supported by the Satellite Situation Center .
HemisphereOptions This class represents hemisphere listing options.
LocationFilter This class represents location filter listing options.
LocationFilterOptions This class represents additional location filter options.
MapLimits This class represents map limit values for an SSC graphing request.
MappedRegionFilterOptions This class represents mapped region filter options.
MapProjectionGraphOptions This class represents options for an SSC Mapped Projection plot request.
OrbitGraphOptions This class represents options for an SSC orbit graphing request.
OutputOptions This class represents output options for an SSC data request.
RegionFilterOptions This class represents region filter options.
RegionOptions This class represents listing options for regions.
Request This class represents a request for the Satellite Situation Center.
Result This class represents the result of a request to the Satellite Situation Center.
SatelliteData This class represents information about a satellite provided by the Satellite Situation Center.
SatelliteDescription This class represents a Satellite Situation Center satellite description.
SatelliteSpecification This class represents a satellite information specification.
SpaceRegionsFilterOptions This class represents space regions filter options.
SpaseObservatoryDescription This class represents a Satellite Situation Center description of a Space Physics Archive Search and Extract (SPASE) Observatory.
TimeSeriesGraphOptions This class represents options for an SSC Time Series plot request.
ValueOptions This class represents value listing options.

Exception Summary

Package gov.nasa.gsfc.spdf.ssc Description

Provides a Web Service interface to NASA's Satellite Situation Center (http://sscweb.gsfc.nasa.gov/).

Package Specification

Satellite Situation Center Web Services (http://sscweb.gsfc.nasa.gov/WebServices/).

Related Documentation

For more information, refer to Satellite Situation Center (http://sscweb.gsfc.nasa.gov/).
